Package entities

Class EditorGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.EditorGame
  • public class EditorGame
extends java.lang.Object
    The object in which all data about the Editor is stored. All slides, decisions, and attributes of slides and decisions are stored here in hashmaps

      • connectSlideAndRenderableSlide

        public void connectSlideAndRenderableSlide​(Slide slide,
                                           GuiSlide guiSlide)
        Connect a single Slide to a single GuiSlide. The GuiSlide is thought to be "representing" the Slide in the GUI.
        Parameters:
        slide - - The slide to become the key of the connection.
        guiSlide - - The GUI version to become the value of the connection.

        guiSlide - - The GuiSlide that corresponds to that new origin.
        decisionId - - The ID of the decision that is changing origin.
